{"tid":1627622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"訓哂未 班勇武搞鳩啲民生設施有乜用","createTime":"2019-10-05T16:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T08:31:51.000Z","uid":115613,"like":4,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6464f6c4582c198e74d5bb24c15a7aca4b40bc9c","tid":1627622,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:49:51.000Z","msg":"其實你地一味搞鳩對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用家都是普通市民<br />\n<br />\n1）美心 <br />\n2）優品360 <br />\n3）中國移動 4）<br />\n4）中銀 <br />\n5）地鐵 <br />\n6）公共設施（交通燈，欄河）<br />\n7）政府建築物（政府合署）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同政府運作沒直接關係之餘又搞到市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔明點解要做啲咁擾民既破壞<br />\n不如又用腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗下點將果目標向番政府"},{"pid":"8c1956a18d80d8b1c089737f788fd3d59ba25ccd","tid":1627622,"uid":19005,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"收皮啦三毛<br />\n搞你老母好冇"},{"pid":"7515afb2180e637a132ae745b8e085d9bfbcb6ce","tid":1627622,"uid":160589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:33:40.000Z","msg":"除左交通燈全部爆得"},{"pid":"c0e2592e50d3c78adcfd48f0e23535f7bf211774","tid":1627622,"uid":160589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:34:04.000Z","msg":"你唔買中資幫襯黃店洗死？"},{"pid":"aa71d49f6b53456af7f740a8c3ecb2633be6f889","tid":1627622,"uid":2582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7515afb2180e637a132ae745b8e085d9bfbcb6ce","tid":1627622,"uid":160589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:33:40.000Z","msg":"除左交通燈全部爆得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:35:39.000Z","msg":"交通燈真係唔搞得"},{"pid":"0539466e868f143e7eb53fac8de6e95ea038318b","tid":1627622,"uid":268860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:40:45.000Z","msg":"收皮<br />\n係象徵意義並唔係間野既本身"},{"pid":"5410a0b34dd99ae5e58b754f5880a087b856155b","tid":1627622,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6464f6c4582c198e74d5bb24c15a7aca4b40bc9c","tid":1627622,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:49:51.000Z","msg":"其實你地一味搞鳩對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用家都是普通市民<br />\n<br />\n1）美心 <br />\n2）優品360 <br />\n3）中國移動 4）<br />\n4）中銀 <br />\n5）地鐵 <br />\n6）公共設施（交通燈，欄河）<br />\n7）政府建築物（政府合署）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同政府運作沒直接關係之餘又搞到市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔明點解要做啲咁擾民既破壞<br />\n不如又用腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗下點將果目標向番政府"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:32:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>對方使用緊急法去立曚面法</strong><br />\n<strong><ins>目的:</ins></strong><br />\n引發更多怒氣, 更多人出街<br />\n1, 使政府立緊急法合理化<br />\n2, 繞過正常程序, 為日後透過緊急法立其它法鋪路 (如凍結資產, 限制通訊, 限制外匯)<br />\n3, 以此為藉口, 推遲或取消區議會, 使原本100%己敗的選舉重新定位<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>解決方案:</ins></strong><br />\n<strong>1, 拉一派, 打一派, </strong>儘量透過這次立緊急法同曚面法帶來的影響争取更多團體的支持, 例如受影響的商家, 目標對準林鄭班子<br />\n<strong>2, 敵進我退</strong>, 當我們知道對家的棋路之後, 就要往<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">相反</span></strong>的方向做, 對家期望會更亂, 我地就要更有秩序, 對家想跟我們決一死戰, 我們就要休息<br />\n<strong>3, 虛實並用</strong>, 不戰而屈人之兵, 若一個吹得起既風而鈎到過百隻狗, 最後班狗無功而回, 不費一兵一卒, 一蚊都唔使比。同樣係政治, 經濟, 媒體, 文宣勇武, 和理非各項必須虛實並用, 目標係不戰而屈人之兵, 以小本勝大本, 令對方管治成本大福上升, 以消耗他們龐大的資源<br />\n<strong>4, 令對方各員產生恐懼</strong>, 不論任何方法, 讓敵方望而遠之, 要他們確切知道幫港共政權做事是有很重的代價"},{"pid":"fea2271370bfd3982b83356a6e1b056bae03486d","tid":1627622,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7515afb2180e637a132ae745b8e085d9bfbcb6ce","tid":1627622,"uid":160589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:33:40.000Z","msg":"除左交通燈全部爆得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:45:57.000Z","msg":"交通燈認同唔好攪"},{"pid":"49349e05033cc49754a402f83c00bc40931bec31","tid":1627622,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:25:11.000Z","msg":"［警世］再係咁運動會完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1627671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1627671</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"301757d01e7a8c098043115a5463361647fb2ef4","tid":1627622,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:26:39.000Z","msg":"罷食罷買咪算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />裝修真是講唔通<br />\n你試下自己屋企比人裝修會點"},{"pid":"4bfdfade60014187e43c43eb126d85a556e58faf","tid":1627622,"uid":65879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"善用不推文回覆 屌鳩樓主呢啲帶風向柒頭皮"},{"pid":"b9ecc4d73216aa6c61f1189171c49a98ebefc1f3","tid":1627622,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bfdfade60014187e43c43eb126d85a556e58faf","tid":1627622,"uid":65879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"善用不推文回覆 屌鳩樓主呢啲帶風向柒頭皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:31:51.000Z","msg":"以事論事姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}